1. install package.json (npm init -y)
2. Install mocha and chai (npm --save-dev mocha chai)
3. new directory file src(file letter-count.js and letter-count.test.js)
4. Install babel package (npm install --save-dev @babel/core @babel/preset-env @babel/register)
5. To run the test (npx mocha "src/**/*.test.js" --recursive --require @babel/register)
